+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: Node.js v24.18.0
+- packageManager: npm 12.0.1
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: scantlings
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright" {scenario}`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --reporter=text npx cucumber-js`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage`
+- plank-inventory: `npx jsdoc -X src/*.js`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: `npx biome lint features/support src`
+- conformance: `npx biome check features/support --config-path scantlings`
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic local-only
+- weather: coverage/weather.json
+- runrecord: coverage/runrecord.json
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: unlocked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber
+- dependency: c8
+- dependency: jsdoc
+- dependency: @biomejs/biome
+- dependency: knip
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
