+Feature: Methodology conformance
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Watchbill shape conformance
+    Given the watchbill file at the project root
+    When the watchbill is validated against the required format
+    Then the watchbill conforms or is absent at the deck at rest
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Perturbation quiescence
+    Given the implementation directories from RIGGING.md
+    When the implementation files are searched for the PERTURBATION token
+    Then no PERTURBATION token is found when the working tree is green
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Stale plank join
+    Given the plank inventory from jsdoc over the implementation directories
+    And the step-usage patterns from the runner
+    When each @planks string is cross-referenced against the step-usage patterns
+    Then every @planks string matches a current step-definition pattern exactly
+    And every @planks-provisional reference names a scenario that still carries @captain
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Plank form check
+    Given the plank inventory extracted from docblock comments on declarations
+    When each @planks and @planks-provisional token is checked for valid form
+    Then every plank token appears as a docblock tag immediately preceding a declaration
+    And no @planks token appears as a line comment or in-body annotation
